         <opener><dateline><date when="1916-11-21">November 21, 1916</date></dateline>
            <address>John Gould Fletcher, Esq.  
               
               37 Crystal Palace Park Road 
               
               Sydenham, England </address></opener>
         
         <p>
            Braithwaite most anxious for your review of me. 
            No matter if printed in “Egoist” too. “Egoist” not copyrighted here and no 
            circulation in America. Send soon as possible. 
            Congratulations on Harriet’s prize, and thanks for article and letter. 
         </p>
         <closer>AMY LOWELL </closer>
